name: THE BLOOD TRIP SERIES Nearly Free Hexaptych Keepsake
description:
This promotional piece for My BLOOD TRIP SERIES was intended to be listed for free, but I was advised against that due to bots scooping up art with prices of zero. If you really want one, and can't afford the 0.001 tez price, please contact Me on Twitter and I will be happy to gift you one from the 100 I've reserved for the series collectors and My own giveaways.

Collectors of the BLOOD TRIP SERIES will have one of these OBJKTs reserved for them. They will be gifted upon request.

3500x2022 JPG

Minted July 24th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or tormential.tez
